name: Foo
body:
### Welcome to FOO
This is a project which focuses on user interaction with system through speech.
Currently under development, but in the near future you'll see a new smart assistant for some of the linux based OSes.
It is mainly useful for somewhat experienced linux users who use terminal frequently.
